Global Evolution of Obesity Research in Children and Youths: Setting Priorities 
for Interventions and Policies.

Tran BX(1)(2), Dang KA(3), Le HT(3), Ha GH(4), Nguyen LH(5), Nguyen TH(6), Tran 
TH(7), Latkin CA(8), Ho CSH(9), Ho RCM(5)(10).

Author information:
(1)Institute for Preventive Medicine and Public Health, Hanoi Medical 
University, Hanoi, Vietnam, bach.ipmph@gmail.com.
(2)Bloomberg School of Public Health, Johns Hopkins University, Baltimore, 
