Outcomes after Ross procedure in adult patients: A meta-analysis and 
microsimulation.

Sibilio S(1), Koziarz A(2)(3), Belley-Côté EP(4)(5), McClure GR(3)(5), MacIsaac 
S(3)(6), Reza SJ(3), Um KJ(4), Lengyel A(3), Mendoza P(3), Alsagheir A(3)(7), 
Alraddadi H(3), Gupta S(3), Schneider AW(8), Patel PM(9), Brown JW(10), Chu 
