Author information:
(1)Facoltá di Medicina e Chirugia, University of Bari "Aldo Moro", Bari, Italy.
(2)Faculty of Medicine, University of Toronto, Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
(3)Department of Surgery, Division of Cardiac Surgery, McMaster University, 
